# Weather API Endpoints

### Get Current Weather by Coordinates
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/weather/current?latitude=-32.5269&longitude=115.7221&units=metric
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Current Weather by Location ID
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/weather/current/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Hourly Forecast by Coordinates
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/weather/forecast/hourly?latitude=-32.5269&longitude=115.7221&hours=24&units=metric
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Daily Forecast by Coordinates
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/weather/forecast/daily?latitude=-32.5269&longitude=115.7221&days=7&units=metric
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Weather Bundle by Coordinates (Current + Forecasts)
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/weather/bundle?latitude=-32.5269&longitude=115.7221&units=metric
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Weather Bundle by Location ID
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/weather/bundle/1
Accept: application/json

